snippet.title: ELDORANTE - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as Makane, a plucky arms merchant, as she tries to make a living while she’s shipwrecked on a strange island.

What better way is there to scrounge up the cash to survive than to find the legendary Golden Land and its untold riches at the bottom of the Dungeon?
